 ('225', '244', 'en_us', 'Worship Schedule', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The cornerstone of Transfiguration’s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God’s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish in the Episcopal Church, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-01 10:13:15', '2018-10-03 16:37:55', 'ed70f2e8-662a-4f6a-a3e9-c4fcbe403c0e'),
