 ('406', '450', 'en_us', 'The Arnold Schwartz Memorial Organ', NULL, 'The Arnold Schwartz Memorial Organ', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p></p><p>This beautiful organ, named in memory of the major donor, Mrs. Marie Schwartz’s late husband, is Opus 92 of C. B. Fisk, Inc.&nbsp;Church of the Transfiguration has an extensive music program including a Men and Boys Choir and a Girls Choir. Our Music Director, Dr. Claudia Dumschat auditions children from all over the city. Those accepted for the choirs receive an excellent musical education and ample opportunities to perform.</p><p></p>', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-23 12:03:04', '2017-09-25 10:02:02', '34a912e5-f65c-4765-bac2-09a8d59499a3'),
 ('407', '451', 'en_us', 'The St. Joseph of Arimathea Chapel', NULL, 'The St. Joseph of Arimathea Chapel', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p></p><p>The ceiling is decorated with renderings of Fra Angelico’s <i>Glory in Paradise</i> and <i>The Last Judgment</i>, painted on canvas panels which have been fitted between the ribs of the plaster vault.&nbsp; Also on view in this chapel is a large painted glass rendering of Raphael’s <i>The </i>T<i>ransfiguration</i>. The entrance to the chapel is graced by polychromed wood carvings of the four Archangels, Uriel, Gabriel, Michael and Raphael.</p><p></p>', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-23 12:11:29', '2017-09-23 12:11:29', '462db9f7-336c-4c2f-94db-f0a4d8fc46bd'),
 ('408', '452', 'en_us', 'Singing Boy and Compline Psalms', NULL, 'The Singing Boy and the Compline Psalms', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>This beautiful statue dates from 1871 and is the work of Franklin Simmons, an American sculptor living in Rome. He seems right at home among the <strong>Compline</strong> <strong>Psalms</strong>. (Compline psalms are prayers said at the end of the day.) Fr. George Hendric Houghton, the founding rector, married a drawing teacher, Caroline Graves Anthon, who painted the psalms on parchment. After her death, Fr. Houghton had her paintings executed in glass as a memorial to her.</p>', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-23 12:12:41', '2017-10-01 12:24:10', '8fe4d172-d88d-47e1-bb1a-c6248396704a'),
 ('411', '455', 'en_us', 'Baptisms', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Holy Baptism <strong>i</strong>s the sacrament welcoming an infant, child, or an adult into the body of Christ!  It is an outward sign of the inward grace of God’s unconditional love for us, and as baptized persons, we are initiated into the full community and responsibilities of the Church.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ahron R. Foster', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2017-09-23 13:50:08', '2017-10-03 23:05:29', '8fb05830-2f66-4bcc-8565-c9cbc9a7ad4b'),
