 ('920', '1046', 'en_us', 'Lenten Quiet Day', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><strong>Join us on Saturday, March 17th, from 10:00 am to 3:00 pm, for a reflection on the spirituality of Episcopal hymns from the Hymnal 1982.  Topics to be covered will include seventeenth-century poems as hymn texts, the hymn texts of Isaac Watts and Charles Wesley, and Anglo-Catholic hymn texts.  The quiet day will be led by Dr. Richard Kieckhefer, Professor of Religious Studies at Northwestern University.  Participants are welcome to attend all or part of the day, and lunch will be provided by the parish.  For more information, please contact Fr. Cheng at <a href=\"mailto:AssociateRector@littlechurch.org\">AssociateRector@littlechurch.org</a>.  To reserve your spot, please email <a href=\"mailto:receptionist@littlechurch.org\">receptionist@littlechurch.org</a>.</strong><br /></p>', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-02-12 15:39:07', '2018-03-19 13:54:22', '4dd6cbf8-0652-4364-bd11-e997c80f83c6'),
