 ('936', '1067', 'en_us', 'Stations of the Cross and Benediction of the Blessed Sacrament', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Stations of the Cross and Benediction of the Blessed Sacrament  will be offered Every Friday night in Lent at 6:30pm. Though brief in length (less than one hour), these beloved devotions have blessed the people of God for centuries, and they continue still.  Please consider these devotions as a possible part of your Lenten discipline. </p>', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-02-16 16:23:23', '2018-03-27 13:32:04', 'f3865a1f-d55b-4a31-ae14-e9205d2d00e1'),
