 ('944', '1075', 'en_us', 'Adult Education', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Our Adult Education forums cover a wide variety of spiritual topics both within the Church and elsewhere. The series hosts a number of guest speakers and facilitators and promises an hour of entertaining and informational learning and discussion. To download the full adult education year\'s brochure, click <a href=\"{asset:1251:url}\">here</a>. </p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-02-28 23:39:54', '2018-10-09 14:20:36', 'b784fea3-7fca-4f4b-b233-6648e0c5d1d8'),
 ('945', '1077', 'en_us', 'Bible Study', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The evening begins with a mass in the chapel at 6:30 pm. Following the mass, the study will begin at 7:00 pm in the common room. Newcomers are always welcome.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-02-28 23:51:29', '2018-10-05 14:01:54', '48401c1d-3613-46c1-9f1a-103f0359f069'),
 ('946', '1079', 'en_us', 'Sunday School', NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Each Sunday, children 4 to 15 are welcome to join us for Sunday school.  We meet during the service: class starts at the first reading (around 11:15 in the common room), and students come back for communion. This week we will study the story of the 10 Commandments.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-03-02 18:15:11', '2018-03-02 19:02:53', '8ab4e4cb-0053-413b-98fd-d896e2802da3'),
