 ('1136', '1282', 'en_us', 'Instructed Eucharist', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>Our next Adult Education series is “Instructed Eucharist” taught by Fr. Cheng. In this series, we will walk through the liturgy of the Holy Eucharist together. Participants will have an opportunity to observe the liturgical actions of the mass from the chancel and to ask Fr. Cheng questions about this liturgy.</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-09-24 14:41:17', '2018-10-09 14:16:46', '8b82d1fe-8063-4852-ab1c-17b18cec9996'),
