 ('1140', '1286', 'en_us', 'The Bible and Economic Justice', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>In this series, we will explore the topic of economic justice in both the Old and New Testaments. Topics to be covered will include biblical laws, narratives, sayings, and parables relating to wealth and poverty.<br /></p>\n<p> \n</p>', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2018-10-09 14:16:38', '2018-10-15 14:56:00', 'cd371808-4a8e-4e2a-a69d-ba593fb814c3'),
