 ('95', '221', '9', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"9\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"The Garden\",\"slug\":\"the-garden\",\"postDate\":1504189343,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"28\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Besides being an oasis of rest and comfort for one and all,&nbsp;the garden provides a small but significant ecological benefit for&nbsp;everyone. The wide expanse of plants, shrubs and trees offsets carbon&nbsp;emissions, and the peace and quiet of the garden offer relief from the&nbsp;city\\u2019s noise pollution.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>Birds stop by to dip their beaks in the fountain.&nbsp;During the week, it\\u2019s a popular lunch spot for people who work in the&nbsp;neighborhood, and on Sundays in warm weather, it\\u2019s the site of coffee hour. This past summer, the garden was enhanced with the generous gift&nbsp;of a young tree from a friend at the nearby James Hotel. Please stop by if&nbsp;you\\u2019re in the neighborhood. You will always be welcome here.<\\/p>\"}}},\"25\":[\"223\"],\"26\":\"\",\"27\":\"\"}}', '2017-08-31 14:22:23', '2017-08-31 14:22:23', 'c682cfd4-e152-4e1b-956e-56cc82d31b2a'),
