ght of my military career, but it has blessed my entire life.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>This Veterans Day I encourage prayers for all those who have served our country with dignity and pride, and may their contributions and sacrifices \\u2013 and the sacrifices of their families \\u2013 be a blessing to us all.<\\/p>\"}}},\"25\":[\"859\"],\"26\":\"Gary Norcross\",\"27\":\" Official U.S. Air Force via VisualHunt.com\",\"70\":\"https:\\/\\/www.flickr.com\\/photos\\/usairforce\\/15785731421\"}}', '2017-11-10 02:36:05', '2017-11-10 02:36:05', '5d4b5e6c-c2a4-4827-8b1c-caf69344f512'),
 ('346', '244', '10', '654', 'en_us', '18', '', '{\"typeId\":\"10\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Worship Schedule\",\"slug\":\"worship-schedule\",\"postDate\":1504260780,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"245\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>At the center of our worship is emphasis on both Word and Table. Little Church clergy are considered <a href=\\\"#\\\">excellent preachers<\\/a>&nbsp;who connect lectionary readings with Biblical context and current challenges with a smattering of personal stories and humor. Transfiguration acolytes do an extraordinary job in ensuring the Eucharist is celebrated with majesty and dignity, and the authentic expertise of <a href=\\\"#\\\">our choirs<\\/a>&nbsp;draws worshippers closer to the love of Jesus Christ through some of the most beloved hymns of the Church.&nbsp;Below is the current worship schedule. Please consider joining us!<\\/p>\"}},\"658\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h2>Preaching and Celebrant Schedule<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>November 2, 2017, 7:00 P.M.&nbsp;(All Souls Day Mass)<\\/strong><br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<br>Preacher:&nbsp;Bishop St. John<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>November 5 (All Saints Day)<\\/strong><br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father Cheng<br>Preacher:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<\\/p><p>November 12&nbsp;<br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father Cheng<br>Preacher: Father van Dooren<\\/p><p>November 19<br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<br>Preacher:&nbsp;Father Cheng<\\/p><p>November 26<br><\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"243\"],\"12\":\"<p>The cornerstone of Transfiguration\\u2019s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God\\u2019s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2017-11-10 20:53:53', '2017-1