DIY\\\"&nbsp;Christmas Pageant<\\/strong><br><br><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>December 24, 10:30 P.M.&nbsp;Midnight Mass<\\/strong><strong>&nbsp;<\\/strong><br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father Cheng<br>&nbsp;Preacher:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>December 25,&nbsp;11:00 A.M. Christmas Day&nbsp;&nbsp;mass<\\/strong><br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<br>&nbsp;Preacher:&nbsp;Father Cheng<br><strong><br><\\/strong><\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"243\"],\"12\":\"<p>The cornerstone of Transfiguration\\u2019s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God\\u2019s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2017-11-15 15:46:46', '2017-11-15 15:46:46', '25a8984f-0e1b-4515-b50e-b3bbc9fed4bb'),
