 ('503', '244', '10', '654', 'en_us', '52', '', '{\"typeId\":\"10\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Worship Schedule\",\"slug\":\"worship-schedule\",\"postDate\":1504260780,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"245\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>At the center of our worship is emphasis on both Word and Table. Little Church clergy are considered <a href=\\\"#\\\">excellent preachers<\\/a>&nbsp;who connect lectionary readings with Biblical context and current challenges with a smattering of personal stories and humor. Transfiguration acolytes do an extraordinary job in ensuring the Eucharist is celebrated with majesty and dignity, and the authentic expertise of <a href=\\\"#\\\">our choirs<\\/a>&nbsp;draws worshippers closer to the love of Jesus Christ through some of the most beloved hymns of the Church.&nbsp;Below is the current worship schedule. Please consider joining us!<\\/p>\"}},\"658\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<h2>Preaching and Celebrant Schedule<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p><strong>March 25, 11:00 A.M. Palm Sunday<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father van Dooren&nbsp;<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Mr. Joshua Heath, Aspirant for Holy Orders<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>March 29, 7:00 P.M. Maundy Thursday<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father Cheng<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Mother Turner<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>March 30, 12:00 P.M. Good Friday<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father van Dooren&nbsp;<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Dr. Kyle Rader<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>March 31, 7:00 P.M.&nbsp;Easter Vigil<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father Cheng<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Father van Dooren<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><strong>April 1, 11:00 A.M. Easter Sunday<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father van Dooren&nbsp;<br>Preacher:&nbsp; Father Cheng<\\/p><p><strong>April 8, The Second Sunday of Easter<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father Cheng<br>Preacher:&nbsp;Dr. Kyle Rader<\\/p><p><strong>April 15: The Third Sunday of Easter<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father van Dooren<br>Preacher: Father Cheng<\\/p><p><br><strong>April 22: The Fourth Sunday of Easter<\\/strong><br>Celebrant: Father Cheng<br>Preacher: Father van Dooren<\\/p><p><strong>April 29:&nbsp;The Fifth Sunday of Easter<\\/strong><br>Celebrant:&nbsp;Father van Dooren<br>Preacher:&nbsp;Brother Bushnell<br><\\/p>\"}}},\"11\":[\"243\"],\"12\":\"<p>The cornerstone of Transfiguration\\u2019s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God\\u2019s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish in the Episcopal Church, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2018-03-19 13:48:02', '2018-03-19 13:48:02', '12e7ae54-65bc-4ed8-9833-2ccaefb00e14'),
