 ('579', '1075', '21', '654', 'en_us', '24', '', '{\"typeId\":\"21\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Adult Education\",\"slug\":\"adult-education\",\"postDate\":1519861140,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"1076\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Our current series is \\\"Instructed Eucharist\\\" taught by Fr. Cheng. In this series, we will walk through the liturgy of the Holy Eucharist together. Participants will have an opportunity to observe the liturgical actions of the mass from the chancel and to ask Fr. Cheng questions about this liturgy.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p> \\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}},\"75\":[],\"11\":[\"909\"],\"12\":\"<p>Our Adult Education forums cover a wide variety of spiritual topics both within the Church and elsewhere. The series hosts a number of guest speakers and facilitators and promises an hour of entertaining and informational learning and discussion. To download the full adult education year\'s brochure, click <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/littlechurch.org\\/images\\/Adult-Education.2018-2019.pdf#asset:1251:url\\\">here<\\/a>. <\\/p>\",\"72\":\"\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2018-10-01 14:51:41', '2018-10-01 14:51:41', 'f5666d7a-79af-485a-a7d0-9bda193bfb45'),
 ('580', '1077', '21', '654', 'en_us', '7', '', '{\"typeId\":\"21\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Bible Study\",\"slug\":\"bible-study\",\"postDate\":1519861860,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"3\":\"\",\"13\":{\"1078\":{\"type\":\"generalSection\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"text\":\"<p>Our Thursday Night Bible Study will resume on September 6. This fall, we will be studying the Letter of Paul to the Romans. Our text will be the New Collegeville Bible Commentary on Galatians and Romans by Robert J. Karris. We will meet for mass in the Holy Family Chapel at 6:30 pm, and our discussion will begin at 7:00 pm in the\\r\\n parish common room. For more information, please email Fr. Cheng at <a href=\\\"mailto:AssociateRector@littlechurch.org\\\">AssociateRector@littlechurch.org<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p> \\r\\n<\\/p>\"}}},\"75\":[],\"11\":[\"918\"],\"12\":\"<p>The evening begins with a mass in the chapel at 6:30 pm. Following the mass, the study will begin at 7:00 pm in the common room. Newcomers are always welcome. The Bible Study will not meet this week, October 4.&nbsp;The study will resume on October 11.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"72\":\"\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2018-10-01 14:52:22', '2018-10-01 14:52:22', '58fd0450-ca82-41d1-9ec6-e41fa8038fb7'),
