figuration\\u2019s spirituality is how we express and demonstrate God\\u2019s inclusive love through liturgy, music, and worship. As an Anglo-Catholic parish in the Episcopal Church, Transfiguration honors traditional liturgy with a full complement of meaningful preaching and music.<\\/p>\",\"27\":\"\",\"70\":\"\"}}', '2018-10-01 15:22:47', '2018-10-01 15:22:47', 'f9978097-09fa-4991-bef0-6d298ba6ab1e'),
